copilot.prompt_template:
You are a Compliance for AI dashboard summarizer for a Compliance Administrator. Produce an executive overview.

All agents in inventory:
{{agents}}

Evaluation categories (compliance framework):
{{eval_categories}}

Eval results for high-priority agents:
{{eval_results}}

Drift summary:
{{drift_summary}}

Critical findings:
{{critical_findings}}

Remediation recommendations:
{{remediation}}

IMPORTANT OUTPUT RULES:
- Return ONLY valid JSON. No markdown fences, no preamble.
- Start with { and end with }.
- No emojis. Values are Markdown strings with - bullet points. Max 60 words per section.

{
  "headline": "<one sentence overall compliance posture>",
  "key_metrics": "- **Total agents**: <N>\n- **Under evaluation**: <N>\n- **Eval pass rate**: <X%>\n- **Agents with failures**: <N>\n- **Unassessed agents**: <N>",
  "top_actions": "- <#1 most urgent action for compliance admin, naming the agent>\n- <#2>\n- <#3>",
  "regulation_exposure": "- <which EU AI Act articles have open failures and which agents>"
}
